item.title: Runing my server
item.dc:creator: @Miss_Doctor Miss_Doctor
item.description:
@Miss_Doctor wrote:

  1. Dont make multiple posts, you made another post with this same information in it
  2. Be more specific…people might not understand what you’re talking about
  3. Luckily for me I READ your previous post, and are you sure you have your router and everything and have port-forwarded etc? No-IPs are for OTHER people to access your server, but you were saying that YOU cant. Empty out the server IP (erase it) and just login with a blank IP. Since you’re the owner, you dont have to type in one.
  4. Also, dont post polls for no reason, I mean, really. Come on now.
